\newlabel{fig:time_wiki}{{2}{7}{Execution time vs.\ $N$ (log-$x$ scale) on \texttt {wiki\_random}. C-Burstsort maintains the flattest scaling; MSD Radix Sort diverges significantly at large $N$ owing to deep recursion on wiki-like prefix structure}{figure.2}{}}
